divs: Sighting DetailsI had been driving my car and my daughter saw a very weird cloud that looked like a tornado so we took out my phone and took a pic. we sent it to our email. later that night we downloaded it to our computer and we saw all these black circles in the cloud about 10 of them. we we making the pic turn negative and you can very much see that they are a solid mass. we were not even looking for these shapes. we could not see them with our eyes at the time at all. this is very exciting
